"com/opensource/gci/2011-12/index.html\">Google Code-In 2011</ulink>. Thanks "
"to Google for sponsoring their excellent work!"
msgstr ""
"Molt de tot açò va ser escrit pels participants de la <ulink url=\"http://"
"code.google.com/opensource/gci/2011-12/index.html\">Google Code-In 2011</"
